      • processWindowEvent

        public void processWindowEvent(java.awt.event.WindowEvent e)
        Refer to JFrame's processWindowEvent method for more info. This method needed to be overridden because we added the SPECIAL_EXIT_ON_CLOSE parameter, which will invoke the exitProgram() method (also made by us), which will exit the program after managing the logger files.
        Overrides:
        processWindowEvent in class javax.swing.JFrame
